name: Thatswzup.com
tag_list: networking, promotion, advertising, clubs, poetry, events, music, entertainment, parties, traveling
overview:
THATSWZUP.COM is a promotional website created and designed to be an entertainmentresource for urban event attendees.

ThatsWzup.com gives those who like to be in-the-know about what is going on in their city, a one-stop shop to find the type of entertainment they maybe looking for. We also provide the entertainment industry with a new vehicle of promotion through the internet. Thatswzup.com’s event-seekers may also look inside different events through our photogallery. We have captured the ambiance and the people at the event for the event-attendees as well as the event-seekers. This provides the attendees with memoirs from the event andshows the seekers the type of event they missed so they don’t miss the next one. Our initial demographic ranges from urban teens to cultured, mature adults, ages 18-45.
